ive green toned cabinets against a white brick wall look of the outback.\" class=\"wp-image-11857\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/16143941\/white-brick-single-wall-kitchen-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/16143941\/white-brick-single-wall-kitchen-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/16143941\/white-brick-single-wall-kitchen-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/16143941\/white-brick-single-wall-kitchen-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A lovely olive green one wall kitchen against a brick wall brings the feel of the outback at home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">What A Wonderful White One Wall Kitchen Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you love a squeaky clean kitchen in white, this single wall kitchen will help you have a clutter-free yet elegant looking space. This kitchen has an inbuilt storage unit for your microwave, that is great to save space. It&#8217;s got drawers so your cutlery can be neatly pushed away in place. Overhead cabinets are provided to store less used utensils. A space for your oven at the bottom is perfect for those who love to bake.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/16144033\/white-one-wall-kitchen-design.jpg\" alt=\"One wall kitchen with white cabinets against splash of grey tinge wall and marble backsplash look elegant \" class=\"wp-image-11858\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/16144033\/white-one-wall-kitchen-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/07\/16144033\/white-one-wall-kitchen-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content